title: Supermarket.Management.v1.1.6-ReUnion
description:
At  the  start  of  the  game you work in a small store and your duties are 
 mainly  filling counters and serving customers. But that is definitely just 
 beginning!  You  can  invest  the  money  earned  into buying and upgrading 
 equipment  that  will  help you organize your workspace effectively. Invest 
 wisely  and  use  little  marketing  tricks  to boost the income! Take your 
 chance  to  make  more money on sales days, when the store sees huge influx 
 of  customers.  Choose  the  right product for each customer, and be quick, 
 they  hate to wait! These levels are designed to challenge and develop your 
 concentration and coordination. 

 1. Extract RARs 
 2. Run ru-sm116.exe to install 
 3. Use SManagement.exe to start 
 4. Have fun!
